source.name: NOLA Live Entertainment Permits - Map
source.description: City of New Orleans, Live Entertainment Permits. Data provided by Bureau of Revenue, 11/30/2012, dataset consisted of 447 records, 441 of which could be geocoded and displayed on the map. Closed/Open status was based on closing date being either pre or post 1/1/2012.
